ons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/github/git-lfs\">git-lfs</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/github/git-lfs\">git-lfs</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/github/git-lfs\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">10.7k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":10726,\"repo\":\"github/git-lfs\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></h2>\n<pre><code>$ git lfs track \"*.mp3\"\nTracking *.mp3\n\n$ git lfs track \"*.zip\"\nTracking *.zip\n\n$ git lfs track\nListing tracked paths\n    *.mp3 (.gitattributes)\n    *.zip (.gitattributes)\n\n$ git lfs untrack \"*.zip\"\nUntracking *.zip\n\n$ git lfs track\nListing tracked paths\n    *.mp3 (.gitattributes)\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T06:35:48.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/git-hooks/git-hooks\">git-hooks</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/git-hooks/git-hooks\">git-hooks</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/git-hooks/git-hooks\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">383</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":383,\"repo\":\"git-hooks/git-hooks\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></h2>\n<pre><code>$ git hooks --install\n$ git hooks\nGit hooks ARE installed in this repository.\n\nListing User, Project, and Global hooks:\n---\n/Users/stevemao/.git_hooks:\n\n/GitHub/git-hooks/git_hooks:\ncommit-msg/signed-off-by \t- Checks commit message for presence of Signed-off-by line.\npre-commit/bsd \t- Check for the BSD license.\n\n/GitHub/git-hooks/.githooks:\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T06:30:00.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ahkscript/awesome-AutoHotkey","categoryHTML":"<h2>Library Distributions</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ahkscript/ASPDM\">ASPDM</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ahkscript/ASPDM\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">58</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":58,\"repo\":\"ahkscript/ASPDM\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - package/stdlib distribution and management from the <a href=\"https://github.com/ahkscript\">ahkscript</a> folks. Trello <a href=\"https://trello.com/b/XVP4M76d/package-stdlib-distribution-and-management\">link</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T05:10:59.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ahkscript/awesome-AutoHotkey","categoryHTML":"<h2>Library Distributions</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/hi5/pAHKlight\">pAHKlight</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/hi5/pAHKlight\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">36</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":36,\"repo\":\"hi5/pAHKlight\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Your Lightweight Guide to AutoHotkey libraries, classes, functions and tools.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T05:10:59.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/mhagger/git-imerge\">git-imerge</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>imerge rebase</h3>\n<pre><code>$ git imerge rebase 4.0\nThe following commits on the to-be-merged branch are merge commits:\n    8e4931ae15971a14897cf347ac50b7d7fe125ac4\n    d7c772142ce663a20210db73d9ad17cc8d59e0d6\n    856df83c77b33029d2ddfb8eecd08efedeadc027\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T03:10:26.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/mhagger/git-imerge\">git-imerge</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>imerge merge</h3>\n<pre><code>$ git imerge merge 4.0\nAttempting automerge of 1-1...success.\nAttempting automerge of 1-6...success.\nAttempting automerge of 1-9...success.\nAttempting automerge of 1-10...success.\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T02:19:02.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/kennethreitz/legit\">legit</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>sync</h3>\n<pre><code>$ git sync\nPulling commits from the server.\nFirst, rewinding head to replay your work on top of it...\nFast-forwarded 4.0 to origin/4.0.\nPushing commits to the server.\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T02:08:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/kennethreitz/legit\">legit</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>switch</h3>\n<pre><code>$ git switch master\nSaving local changes.\nSaved working directory and index state On developement: Legit: stashing before switching branches.\nHEAD is now at f0fc4c7 Merge branch 'development'\nSwitching to master.\nYour branch is up-to-date with 'origin/master'.\nRestoring local changes.\nOn branch master\nYour branch is up-to-date with 'origin/master'.\nChanges not staged for commit:\n  (use \"git add &#x3C;file>...\" to update what will be committed)\n  (use \"git checkout -- &#x3C;file>...\" to discard changes in working directory)\n\n\tmodified:   package.json\n\nno changes added to commit (use \"git add\" and/or \"git commit -a\")\nDropped stash@{0} (86f5dc9066ff9f69c01c77e2f5a55643ad19f8f2)\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T02:08:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/kennethreitz/legit\">legit</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>publish</h3>\n<pre><code>$ git publish\n   4.0                        (published)\n   changelog                  (published)\n   everything-is-not-awesome  (published)\n*  master                     (unpublished)\nBranch None not found, using current branch master\nPublishing master.\nBranch master set up to track remote branch master from origin.\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T02:08:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/kennethreitz/legit\">legit</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>unpublish</h3>\n<pre><code>$ git unpublish master\nUnpublishing master.\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T02:08:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/kennethreitz/legit\">legit</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>branches</h3>\n<pre><code>$ git branches\n   4.0                        (published)\n   development                (unpublished)\n   everything-is-not-awesome  (published)\n*  master                     (published)\n   old-master                 (published)\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T01:39:45.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"sindresorhus/amas","categoryHTML":"<h4>Ask these people anything!</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Qix-/ama\">JD Ballard</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Qix-/ama\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":4,\"repo\":\"Qix-/ama\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Idaho native, Chalk collaborator, sunshine burns us. Likes hypotheticals, dislikes bees.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T01:04:00.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/spotify/git-test\">git-test</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/spotify/git-test\">git-test</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/spotify/git-test\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">190</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":190,\"repo\":\"spotify/git-test\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></h2>\n<pre><code>$ git test -v\n4.0 ^origin/4.0 ^origin/master will test        2 commits\niter commit  tree    result\n0000 57af4b0 f5ef0d8 pass (cached)\n0001 10ed389 434370f pass\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T01:03:50.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/tkrajina/git-plus\">git-plus</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>multi</h3>\n<pre><code>$ git multi\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nExecuting git status -s\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nchalk:\n\t M package.json\n\ngulp:\n\t D index.js\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T00:55:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/tkrajina/git-plus\">git-plus</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>relation</h3>\n<pre><code>$ git relation origin/4.0\nHEAD and origin/4.0 DIVERGED, common point is 657213a52d5e9c19b85df6a42f76341a98c08ae8\n\nCommits from 657213a52d5e9c19b85df6a42f76341a98c08ae8 to HEAD:\nError retrieving log 657213a52d5e9c19b85df6a42f76341a98c08ae8..HEAD\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T00:55:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/tkrajina/git-plus\">git-plus</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>old-branches</h3>\n<pre><code>$ git old-branches -d 10\nBranch 4.0 is older than 10 days (139.86)!\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T00:55:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/iwata/git-now\">git-now</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/iwata/git-now\">git-now</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/iwata/git-now\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">146</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":146,\"repo\":\"iwata/git-now\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></h2>\n<pre><code>$ git now\n[master 1bd9ce8] [from now] 2015/08/27 10:39:10\n 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)\n$ git log\ncommit 1bd9ce878a76140f7db95afd9cfd4d7befbc7243\nAuthor: Steve Mao &#x3C;maochenyan@gmail.com>\nDate:   Thu Aug 27 10:39:10 2015 +1000\n\n    [from now] 2015/08/27 10:39:10\n\n    diff --git a/package.json b/package.json\n    index 8768569..540523a 100644\n    --- a/package.json\n    +++ b/package.json\n    @@ -1,7 +1,7 @@\n     {\n       \"name\": \"gulp\",\n       \"description\": \"The streaming build system\",\n    -  \"version\": \"3.9.0\",\n    +  \"version\": \"3.10.0\",\n       \"homepage\": \"http://gulpjs.com\",\n       \"repository\": \"gulpjs/gulp\",\n       \"author\": \"Fractal &#x3C;contact@wearefractal.com> (http://wearefractal.com/)\",\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T00:41:09.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"stevemao/awesome-git-addons","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/aanand/git-up\">git-up</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/aanand/git-up\">git-up</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/aanand/git-up\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2.6k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":2623,\"repo\":\"aanand/git-up\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></h2>\n<pre><code>$ git up\nFetching origin\n4.0       fast-forwarding...\nchangelog ahead of upstream\nmaster    fast-forwarding...\nreturning to 4.0\n</code></pre>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T00:37:21.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"RomanTsegelskyi/rbooks","categoryHTML":"<h2>Machine Learning</h2>","itemHTML":"<h4>Machine Learning with R <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Machine-Learning-R-Brett-Lantz/dp/1782162143\">[Amazon]</a> <a href=\"http://shop.oreilly.com/product/9781782162148.do\">[O'Reilly]</a></h4>\n<img src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/518PBAYk%2BxL._SX404_BO1,204,203,200_.jpg\" width=\"200px\">\n<p>\"Machine Learning with R\" is a practical tutorial that uses hands-on examples to step through real-world application of machine learning. Without shying away from the technical details, we will explore Machine Learning with R using clear and practical examples. Well-suited to machine learning beginners or those with experience. Explore R to find the answer to all of your questions.</p>","updatedAt":"2015-08-27T00:31:19.000Z"}]}},"pageContext":{"type":"day","from":1440633600000,"to":1440719999999,"previousId":"2015-08-28","nextId":"2015-08-26","nextName":"Aug 26th, 2015","previousName":"Aug 28th, 2015"}},"staticQueryHashes":["228695001","2744905544","2828988102"]}